Program: Outlook
Title: How Altruism May not be Selfless
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbrqm
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
Explaining altruism, and how an experiment showed that those who give receive more back. Also, a teacher in Stockholm recalls his memorable pupil. Learning a musical instrument. Round dome vs spires in architecture. Presenter: Frederick Dove.